---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About Rachel" description="Marketing, content & documentation consultant with 20+ years of experience.">
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-inner">
      <p class="t-label eyebrow">Marketing strategist, advisor &amp; mentor</p>
      <h1 class="display-headline">25 years of making complex products buyable.</h1>

      <div class="bio-rows">
        <div class="bio-row">Marketing, content &amp; documentation consultant</div>
        <div class="bio-row">Expert in GTM strategy, messaging, and technical storytelling</div>
        <div class="bio-row">Passionate about cyber, HR tech, dev tools, emerging tech &amp; more</div>
        <div class="bio-row">Authentic leader successful in building high-performing teams</div>
        <div class="bio-row last">Thought leader, writer, and mentor</div>
      </div>

      <p class="bio-body">With 20+ years of experience writing for companies like Cisco, Snyk, and Pentera, I help brands stand out in their market. My expertise spans writing for developers and executives, crafting docs, microcopy, blog posts, scripts, and more — consulting on content strategy, tools, and methodologies across multiple industries and verticals.</p>

      <div class="cta-row">
        <a href="https://app.enhancv.com/share/50e871a8/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-ink">View Full CV</a>
        <a href="/lets-meet/" class="btn btn-voltage">Let's meet</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="companies-section">
    <div class="about-inner">
      <p class="t-label companies-eyebrow">Customers &amp; employers</p>
      <div class="logo-grid">
        <div class="logo-slot" style="width:72px;"></div>
        <div class="logo-slot" style="width:56px;"></div>
        <div class="logo-slot" style="width:80px;"></div>
        <div class="logo-slot" style="width:88px;"></div>
        <div class="logo-slot" style="width:68px;"></div>
        <div class="logo-slot" style="width:92px;"></div>
        <div class="logo-slot" style="width:96px;"></div>
        <div class="logo-slot" style="width:76px;"></div>
      </div>
      <p class="companies-names t-mono">Cisco · Snyk · Cycode · BlinkOps · Pentera · Coro · Geotab / Surfsight · Visual Layer</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    padding: 88px var(--pad-page) 64px;
  }

  .about-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    color: var(--c-pink-hot);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .display-headline {
    font-family: 'Schibsted Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 60px);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--c-ink);
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 48px;
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .bio-rows {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--c-hairline-soft);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .bio-row {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-hairline-soft);
    padding: 18px 0;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-family: 'Schibsted Grotesk', sans-serif;
    color: var(--c-body);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .bio-row.last {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .bio-body {
    font-family: 'Schibsted Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--c-body);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 0 40px;
  }

  .cta-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .companies-section {
    padding: 56px var(--pad-page) 80px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--c-hairline);
  }

  .companies-eyebrow {
    color: var(--c-muted);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .logo-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 32px 40px;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .logo-slot {
    height: 18px;
    background: var(--c-ink);
    border-radius: 3px;
    opacity: 0.55;
  }

  .companies-names {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--c-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
</style>
